Usage: EasySave.exe [OPTIONS] [ARGUMENTS]

OPTIONS:
      --save      Save (default)
  -h, --help      Display this help message
  -v, --version   Version

ARGUMENTS:
  N               One single save (from 1 to 5 included)
  N-M             Range of saves (from N to M)
  N;M             Multiple saves (N and M)
